<br>
Guilds like SR, Watchers, Enshadowed, ET.. hell, even the future &quot;uber&quot; guilds like LOA, LA, Blood Inferno, and the list goes on.. They have endorsed, embraced and helped enforce reservations this long. Every time you call one of them greedy, your slapping them in the face.<br>
<br>
Reservations *exist* because of these people, and countless others. Don't call anyone greedy for seeing that the system we had, which was optimized for maybe 10-12 guilds in the beginning, needs to be tweaked now that we have several hundred guilds and literally *thousands* of people using. Please do not be short sighted, or refuse to look at the situation from more than just your own point of view.<br>
<br>
